ek aadmi kii car parking se chori ho gayi. do din baad dekha to car waapas usee jagah parking main hi khadi thi. andar ek lipapha tha usame ek maafinama tha *"maan kii tabiyat achaanak bighad jane se raaton raat bade aspataal lekar janaa aavashyak tha.* *lekin itani raat main or chhuttiyon ke sijan main gadee mili nahin isi vajah se aapaki gaadi ko upyog main lenaa padaa.* *aapako takalif dene ke liye khed he gadee main jitna petrol tha utana hi he. uskaa laac bhi thik kara diya he .* *aapako gaadi kii madad ke evaj main kal raat "bahubali 2" cinema kii 5 tikets aapke parivaar ke liye car main rakhen hai.* *mujhe bade dil ke saath maaf kariye ye vinati he aapse !!* chitthee main story original lagane se or gaadi jaisi kii taisi waapas sahi salaamat milane se parivaar shant ho gaya or duusare din "bahubali 2" dekhne chalaa gaya 4parijan or ek mitra; aakhir 6 lakh kii gaadi waapas jo mil gayi thi . film dekhakar raat ko waapas lautaa to ghar kaa darwaja tutaa hua tha. andar jaakar dekha to sab keemtee saamaan gaayab tha. kareeb 25-30 lakh kii chori ho gayi thi . baahar teble par ek lipapha tha, jisame likhaa tha, *\u201cab pataa chalaa ki katappa ne bahubali ko kyon maaraa ??\u201d*

deshbhumi uttrakhand kii pehali janhiton ke liye samarpit sarkaar ko giraane kii bhul karne vaale sattalolupu netaaon ko roke modi naitikta kii duhai dene vaale kyon tiwari, bahuguna ke kushasan, kumbh va starjia prakaran par mook rahe nai dilli(pyau). loksabhaa chunaav 2014 main desh kii janata ne jahaan manamohani kushasan se mukti ke liye narendra modi kaa aitihaasik samarthan de kar purna bahumat se sattashin karne kaa kaary kiya. desh kii janata dwaara sushasan kii aash main diye is samarthan kii aad main kuch padlolupu uttrakhand bhaajapai netaa devbhumi uttrakhand main rajya gathan ke 13 saal baad sattashin pehali janhiton ke liye samarpit harish ravat kii sarkaar ko giraane ke liye narendra modi ko gumraah kar rahe hai. aaj uttrakhand kii janata ne kendra main asin rahi manamohani kushasan ko ukhaad phenkane va desh main sushasan ko sthapit karne ke liye narendra modi ko khulaa samarthan diya he. na kii pradesh main rajya gathan ke baad pehali baar janaankankshaon ko saakaar karne ke liye samarpit ho kar kaam kar rahi harish ravat kii sarkaar ko giraane ke liye. desh ke jananaayak modi ko is baat kaa ahsaas hoga ki uttrakhand main ab tak jitani bhi bhaajapa va congress kii sarkarein rahi (tiwari, khandudi, nishank va bahuguna aadi )unhone pradesh kii janaankankshaon ko saakaar karne ke bajaay unka galaa ghontne kaa kaam kiya. aise janhiton ko nirmamata se raundne vaale kushasako va gat varsh kaa kedarghati main aayi traasadee se ubarne main kargar sabit ho rahe pradesh ke vartmaan mukhyamantri harish ravat kii sarkaar ko kaaphi aashaayein he. jis prakaar se mukhyamantri harish ravat ne apane chand mahine ke shashan main kai jamini kaary karke janata ke dammagaate vishwaas ko patari main laane kaa kaam kiya. uske baad pradesh kii janata ko laga ki pehali baar apni koi sarkaar sattashin hui he. khaskakar jo sarkaar garesenn ke sapane ko saakaar karne ke liye krit sankalpit ho, jo sarkaar kii janata ke sarkaron se utar chuke vishwaas ko patari par laa sakati he, jo sarkaar bhrashtachari naukarshahon va netaaon ke gathjod par ankush laga saktaa he. jo uttrakhand janaankankshaon ko saakaar karne ke liye krit sankalpit he. nahin to purvavarti tiwari, khandudi, nishank va bahuguna kii sarkaron ne jis nirmamata se pradesh kii janaankakshaon ko raundne kaa kaam kiya tha usase janata kaa vishwaas hi tut gaya tha. jis prakaar se purvavarti sarkaron ne mujfarnagarkand ke doshiyon ko sangrakshan dene, gairsann par chhalane, jansankhya par aadhaarit parisemen thopane, bhrashtachar ke krityon se janata ko chhalane kaa kaary hi kiya. pradesh kii janata main abhi kumbh ghotaale va starjia ghotaale va bahuguna ke kushasan ke dansh abhi bhi vyathit kar rahe he. aise main naitikta kii duhai dene vaale bhaajapa ke tamaam netaa chaahe khandudi ho yaa nishank yaa satpal maharaj inamen se kisi ko bhi naitikta kii duhai dene kaa haq nahin he. ye netaa bataaye ki ye log starjia, kumbh prakaran , tiwari va bahuguna ke kushasan aadi par kyon sharmnaak mook rakhe hue the. kyon inhone mujfarnagar kand-94 ke gunaahagaaron va mulaayam ke kaharon ko sangrakshan dene kaa kaam kiya. kyon ne netaa apane sankeern swaarth ke peeche pradesh ko ek aam aadmi subah jaagane ke baad sabase pehle toilet jaataa he, baahar aa kar sabun se haath dhota he, daant brush karata he, nahaata he, kapade pahanakar taiyaar hota he, akhbaar padhta he, naashtaa karata he, ghar se kaam ke liye nikal jaataa he, baahar nikal kar rickshaw karata he, phir local bas yaa train main yaa apni sawari se offis pahunchataa he, vahaan puraa din kaam karata he, saathiyon ke saath chaay peetaa he, shaam ko vaapis ghar ke liye nikalataa he, ghar ke raste main bacchon ke liye toffee, bivi ke liye mithai vagairah letaa he, mobile main richarge karwaata he, or anek chote mote kaam nipataate hue ghar pahunchataa he, ab aap bataaiye ki use din bhar main kahin koi "hindu" yaa "musalmaan" mila ? kya usne din bhar main kisi "hindu" yaa "musalmaan" par koi atyaachaar kiya ? usko jo din bhar main mili wo the akhbaar vaale bhaiya, doodh vaale bhaiya, rickshaw vaale bhaiya, bas conductor, offis ke mitra, aangtuk, paan vaale bhaiya, chaay vaale bhaiya, toffee kii dukaan vaale bhaiya, mithai kii duukaan vaale bhaiya jab ye sab log bhaiya or mitra hai to inamen "hindu" yaa "musalmaan" kahan he ? "kya din bhar main usne kisi se poocha ki bhai, tu "hindu" he yaa "musalmaan" ? agar tu "hindu" yaa "musalmaan" he to main teri bas main safar nahin karunga, tere haath kii chaay nahin piyunga, teri dukaan se toffee nahin kharidoongaa, kya usne sabun, doodh, aataa, namak, kapade, juute, akhbaar, toffee, mithai kharidte samay kisi se ye sawaal kiya tha ki ye sab banane or ugane vaale "hindu" hai yaa "musalmaan" ? "jab hamaari rosemara kii zindagi main milane vaale log "hindu" yaa "musalmaan" nahin hote to phir kya vajah he ki "chunaav" aate hi ham "hindu" yaa "musalmaan" ho jate hai ? samaaj ke teen jehar tivi kii bematlab kii bahes rajanetao ke jahrile bol or kuch kambakht logo ke soshal media ke bhadakaau massej inase dur rahe to shaayad bahut had tak samasya to hal ho hi jaayegi. share karen chhalaavon se bachein sirf padhe likhe log share kare jaahil log delete kar de padhaa likhaa samajhakar hi aapako bheja he

bharat kii jidipi pe kuch kahana chahta hoon, padhiyegaa. congress sarkaar ke vaqt vittiya varsh 2013-2014 main bharat kii jidipi 4.7 thi, jiskaa hawala dete hue us vaqt ke ghoshit pradhanmantri shri modi ji ne manmohan sarkaar pe kadi tippanee karte hue janata se apane haq main vot maanga tha, or bharat kii arthvyavastha ko behatar karne kaa vaada kiya tha, jise sach maanate hue janata ne unhen vot diya or bharat ke ujjwal bhavishya ke liye unhen pradhanmantri banaaya. pradhanmantri banane ke baad janvari 2015 main modi sarkaar main bharat kii jidipi ke gananaa kaa swarup hi badal daalaa or jo jidipi manmohan sarkaar ke vaqt 4.7 thi vahi jidipi gananaa kaa swarup badal die jane ke kaaran modi sarkaar ke vaqt 6.9 ho gai. us vaqt ke RBI governor raghuram rajan ne isape kadi tippanee karte hue kaha tha:- "maan lijie ki ek bachche kii maa apane bachche kii dekhbhaal ke liye duusare bachche kii maa ko 500 rupee detii he. duusare bachche kii maa bhi pehle bachche kii maa ko apane bachche kii dekhbhaal ke liye 500 rupee detii he. jidipi kii gananaa main isse 1000 rupee jud jaayenge. lekin, kya sachmuch isse arthvyavastha behatar hui, kyonki donon kaa bhugtan to aapas main cat kar shunya ho gaya!" maujuuda vaqt main notebandi ke baavjood modi sarkaar ne bharat kii jidipi 7.0 bataai he, agar manmohan sarkaar ke vaqt ke jidipi gananaa ke swarup se dekha jaae to ye jidipi 4.7 ke aas paas hi he. yahan bhi modi sarkaar ne ham janata ko phir se baari dhokhaa diya he, bharat main bajet satr hameshaa march main shuru hua he, vajah he vittiya varsh kaa 1 april se shuru hona, jahaan farvari ke akhir main maujuuda vittiya varsh kii aakhri report aati he, jiske aankadon ko dhyaan main rakh kar aane vaale vittiya varsh ke liye bajet banaaya jaataa he. dhyaan dene vaali baat ye he ki, modi sarkaar ne saal 2017-2018 kaa bajet saal 2016-2017 ke teesri timahi ke aadhaar par hi bana liya, jisame notebandi se hue nuksaan kaa koi zikr nahin he, kyonki notebandi ke baad vaali aakhri timahi kaa data 28 farvari 2017 ko aayaa he. ab aap ye sonchiye aap bevaqoof kab bane? jab aapane modi ko vot diya tab, yaa ab, jab modi sarkaar aankado kaa swarup badal kar hamen bevaqoof bana rahi he. ham to aaj bhi 69% logon main hi shumaar hai jinhone bevaqoof banane se inkaar kar diya tha, par aap 31% logon kii bevaqufi kaa nuksaan pure bharat ko jhelana pad rahaa he, apane chhetra ke bijepi bharat jitna adhik barbaad ho rahaa he utana hi bharat ko barbaad karne kii england kii niti safal ho rahi he. bharat ke bhrashtachari netaaon, pakistan ke shaskaon or aatankwaadiyon ke maalik ek hi hai. inke asli maalik to ve videshi shaasha hai jin-jin england + america + switzraland + dubai aadi deshon main bharat or pakistan ke bhrashtachari netaaon ne apane-apane deshon se lutaa hua dhan rakhaa hua he. un videshi shaskaon ke dabaav main hi bhrashtachari netaa bharat ko barbaad karne main lage hue hai kyonki bhrashtachari netaaon par ye dabaav rahata he ki yadi inhone videshi shaskaon ke anusaar kaam nahin kiya to videshi shaasha bharat ke bhrashtachari netaaon kii sampatti jabt karne ke saath-saath sampatti kii jaankaree bharat ke nagarikon ko de denge. bharat kii bhrashtachari sarkarein raksha, krishi or aarthik niti waisi hi banaate hai jaisaa ki videshi shaasha chaahate hai. isiilie bhartiya sena kaa atyaadhunikaran nahin kiya gaya, swadeshi krishi ko barbaad karne ke naye-naye tareeke dhunde ja rahe hai taaki videsh se anaaj aayaat karen bhrashtachari sarkarein, swadeshi takanic vaale udyog ko praathamikta nahin di ja rahi he or videsh kii companiyon ko praathamikta di ja rahi he. petrol pump, taabut, vyapam, dilli MCD, DDCA aadi ghotaale karne waalo ne or boforce, 2ji, koyala aadi ghotaale karne waalo ne desh ko luutane or barbaad karne main koi kasar baaki nahin chodi. deshhit ko peeche chhodkar jabatak ham apane-apane vyaktigat swaarth ke kaaran apni-apni raajnneetik party/netaa ko praathamikta dete rahenge tabatak ham yun hi barbaad hote rahenge. bhaashanon se or media dwaara banavaai gai chhavi se bhramit naa hokar dekhnaa hamen ye chahie ki kisi bhi raajnneetik party/netaa ne sarkaar main aane ke baad deshhit main kaam kya kiya. ek dambhi deshbhakti kaa or duusare secularism kaa dhol bajaate raho, apni-apni raajnneetik party/netaa kaa raag alapate raho or apane desh ko barbaad karte raho. yahi ho rahaa he.

meerut ke civil lines ilaake main retoverd karnal devendra kumaar ke ghar chhapemari main 150 se adhik hathiyaar jisamen 40 raifal, 20 pistal, 2 lakh kaartoos, 1 karod nakad, 117 kilo pratibandhit maance mila he. media ko jis tarah se is khabar ko dikhaanaa tha usne vaise nahin dikhaaya. ab maan lijie retoverd karnal koi musalmaan hota. to desh kaa haal kaisaa hota? -NIA turant is maamle kii padtaal ke liye meerut pahunch chuki hoti. - grahamantri is puure maamle par pradhanmantri ko shwetapatr jari kar chuke hote. - ghar ke maalik, karnal ke rishtedaar, padosi or kutton tak ko police giraftaar kar chuki hoti. -media ab tak karnal ke taar ISIS, alqaida, hijbul, pakistan se jod chuki hoti. zee news har ek ghante main is par special report kar chukaa hota. abeepi news darjanon dibet karvaa chukaa hota. - rashtriya suraksha par likhane vaale sampadak/patrkaar ab tak us retoverd karnal kii bivi ke paas kitne peticot or kitne salwar kameez hai us par likh chuke hote. -soshal media par 'saare musalmaan aatankwaadi nahin hote lekin saare aatankwaadi musalmaan hote hai' kahana shuru ho gaya hota. farji news websites jeenyu ko iskaa zimmedaar bana chuke hote. chunki giraftaar karnal kaa naam devendra kumaar he na ki ashraf hossain isliye maahaul shant he. media aaraam se he. desh kii suraksha ko koi khatara nahin he. meerut pakistan nahin bana he. jai bharat. jai modi. jai media. jai rashtrawaad.

jab kanoonee rup se vayask hue, tab tak indira ji ne sikkim ko desh main jod liya tha \u2022 modi jab apni patni ko chhod kar ghar se bhaage the tab indira ji ne pehla parmaanu visphot kar liya tha \u2022 jab modi apni maan ko bina bataaye ghar se nikal liye the tab tak desh anaaj ke bare main aatm nirbhar ho gaya tha. \u2022 modi ko jab cycle chalaa rahe the bharat hawaii jahaaj or helicopter banane laga tha \u2022 modi ko jab bolnaa nahin aata tha rajeev gandhi ne roj ek tivi tower kaa udghaatan karke desh ke ghar ghar main tivi pahunchaa diya tha. \u2022 modi jab sangh karyaalay main jhaadu lagaate the, tab desh main super computer, televijan or suchana kranti ( Information Technology) puure bharat main sthapit ho chukaa tha \u2022 modi jab gujarat main keshubhai patel or shankar singh waghela ke kilaaf saazishen rach rahe the, tab desh main aarthik udaarikaran manmohan singh ji laa chuke the \u2022 jab modi pradhan mantri pad kii shapath le rahe the tab tak bharat sarvaadhik videshi mudra ke kosh vaale pratham 10 rashtron main shaamil ho chukaa tha \u2022 inke alaava chandra yaan, mangal mishan , GSLV, metro, mono rail, antarrashtriya hawaii adde, newclear pandubbi, dheron missile,prithvi, agni, naag darjanon parmaanu sayantr, chetak helicopter, mig tejas, drone, arjuna tanks, dhanush top, missile yukt vimaan, ai en es vikrant vimaan vaahak pot ye sab uplabdhiyaan desh ne modi ke pradhanmantri banane ke pehle hasil kar lee thi. apni ankhen kholo jaankaree se munh mat modiye. kisi bhi netaa ko apana bhagwaan mat banaaiye.

ab desh kii janata haath malati rah jaaegi, kyonki kaala dhan to waapas ab nahin aane vaala he. ab yah bhi pataa nahin chal paaegaa ki ve koun-koun se karnadhaar or vartmaan sarkaar ke pirya hai, jinhone desh kaa paisa lut kar apane swiss bainkon ke khato main jamaa kiya he. bharat sarkaar ne switzraland kii sarkaar ke saath milakar ye ek sharmnaak or desh virdohi karnama kiya he, lekin desh main isaki charchaa tak nahin he? yah bhi ek raaj he ki, kaale dhan ke mudde par ab tak bharat sarkaar yah kahati aa rahi thi ki, switzraland ke kaanoon kii vajah se hamen in khaaton ke bare main jaankaree nahin mil rahi he. to bharat sarkaar ko yah qaraar karnaa chahie tha ki, ab tak jitne bhi khate chal rahe hai, unki jaankaree mil sake, lekin sarkaar ne aisa nahin kiya. isse yahi saaf hota he ki, sarkaar kaale dhan ke maamle par desh ke logon ko gumraah kar rahi he. darasal, kaale dhan ke maamle par sarkaar sochati kuch he, bolti kuch he or karti kuch or he. press conference or media ke saamne aate hi sarkaar chalaane vaale sadhu ban jate hai. mantri or netaa bhrashtachar se ladane kii kasame khate hai. jhootha vishwaas dilaane kii koshish karte hai ki ve kaale dhan ko waapas laane ke sabhi tarah ke prayaas kar rahe hai. asaliyat yah he ki sarkaar desh kii janata or court ke saamne ek ke baad ek jhooth bol rahi he. jabaki parde ke peeche se vah vah desh kii janata ke saath dhokhaa kar rahi he.

chunavi chande kaa paardarshee khel or ankhon par pardaa !! march main jab vitt mantri loksabhaa main vitt vidheyak pesh karte hue yah kah rahe the azaadi ke sattar saal baad bhi desh raajnneetik dalon ke chandon k liye paardarshee prakriya viksit nahin kar sakaa he jo mukt or nishpaksh chunaavon k system ke liye anivaary he. zyaadaatar logon kaa dhyaan isi nek baat par rahaa ki sattar saal baad kuch nayaa or behatar ho rahaa he lekin vitt mantri jis system kii buniyaad rakh rahe the, uske hi paardarshee hone par sawaal uthne lage hai. mukhya chunaav ayukta naseem zadi ne kaha he ki chunavi chande main korparet compinyon kii taraf se chanda dene kii seemaa hataane se paardarshita ko nuksaan pahunchaa he. nae kanoon ke anusaar karporate companiyaan apane munaafe kaa kitna bhi pratishat kisi dal ko chande ke taur par de sakati hai. pehle wo 7.5 pratishat se zyaada nahin de sakati thim or unhen apane bahikhaate main darj karnaa hota tha taaki uski audit ho sake. ab unhen yah chhot hogi ki bahikhaate main bhi darj na karen ki kise chanda diya he or kitna diya he. na bhi dimaag lagaakar sochen to paardarshee system banane ke naam par isse bada chal kya ho saktaa he. namis zadi sahab kaa jo bayaan indian express main chapa he, uski bhashaa chintaa kii he jabaki ve baat khatare kii kar rahe hai. zaahir he unki apni seemaa yaa maryaada hogi magar khatare kii bhashaa khatare kii honi chahie. company act main badlaav se ab hoga ye ki koi company kisi party ko chanda degi, badale main use theka milegaa, theke kaa project paanch sau kaa hazaar karod kar diya jayega taaki use pachaas kii jagah teen sau karod kaa munafa ho sake or yah paisa sidhe kisi party ke khate main chalaa jayega yaa kisi netaa kaa ho jayega. mukhya chunaav ayukta ne kaha he ki is sudhaar se bahut si farzi companiyaan ban jaaengi jinke zariye partiyon ko chanda diya jane lagegaa. is vakt sarkaar farzi companiyon ke kilaaf karrwai kar rahi he jinhen ham cell company kehete hai magar is karrwai kaa ye matlab nahin he ki cell company banane kii sambhaavna samaapt kar di gai he. jo puraani hai unke kilaaf karrwai kar vaahvahee luti ja rahi he. in companiyon ke zariye videshi paisa bhi bharat ke chunaavon main bahane lagegaa. yah vakt hi aisa he ki sarkaar kuch bhi karti he, logon ko andeh kam hota he. yahi is sarkaar kii sabase badi kamyaabi he. varna pehle 20,000 tak chanda dene vaale kaa naam darj nahin hota tha. ab ise ghataakar 2000 kar diya gaya he. sunne main to ye krantikari kadam lagata he magar saadhaaran dimaag se samajha ja saktaa he ki do hazaar ke das note alag alag naam se diye ja sakate hai. sarkaar har baat main digital transection kii vakaalat karti he, sabase pehle wo tamaam raajnneetik dalon ke liye sau fisadi digital chande kii baat kyon nahin laati he. 2000 kii seemaa ko bhi khatm kar dena chahie. khushi kii baat ye he ki sabhi raajnneetik dal centre sarkaar ke is badlaav kaa virodh nahin kar rahe hai. aap paardarshee paardarshee kaa jaap sunate rahiye.

'saleem-javed' kii jodi kii likhi hui filmon ko dekhen, to unamem aapako aksar bahut hi chaalaaki se hindu dharm kaa majaak tathaa muslim / isai dharm ko mahaan dikhaaya jaataa milegaa. inaki lagbhag har film main ek mahaan muslim charitra avashya hota he or hindu mandir kaa majaak tathaa sant ke rup main paakhandee thag dekhne ko milte hai. 1/ film "sholay" main dharmendra bhagwaan shiv kii aad lekar "hema malini" ko premjaal main phasaana chahta he, jo yah sabit karata he ki mandir main log ladkiyaan chhedane jate hai. isi film main e. ke. hangal itnaa pakkaa namaji he ki bete kii laash ko chhodkar, yah kahkar namaaj padhne chal detaa he ki use or bete kyon nahin die qurbaan hone ke liye. 2/ "diwaar" kaa amitabh bachchan naastik he or wo bhagwaan kaa prasad tak nahin khaanaa chahta he, lekin 786 likhe hue bille ko hameshaa apni jeb main rakhata he, or wo billaa hi baar-baar amitabh bachchan kii jaan bachaata he. 3/ "zanjeer" main bhi amitabh naastik he or jaya, bhagwaan se naaraaz hokar gaanaa gaati he, lekin sherkhan ek sachcha insaan he. 4/ film 'shaan" main amitabh bachchan or shashi kapur sadhu ke vesh main janata ko thagte hai, lekin isi film main "abdul" aisa sachcha insaan he jo sachai ke liye jaan de detaa he. 5/ film "kranti" main mata kaa bhajan karne vaala raja (pradeep kumaar) gaddaar he or karimkhan (shatrughna sinha) ek mahaan deshbhakt, jo desh ke liye apni jaan de detaa he. 6/ amar-akbar-anthoni main teenon bacchon kaa baap kishanlaal ek khooni smagaller he lekin unke bacchon (akbar or anthoni) ko paalane vaale muslim or isai mahaan insaan he. 7/ kul milakar aapako, 'saleem-javed' kii filmon main, hindu naastik milegaa yaa phir dharm kaa uphaas karata hua koi karnama dikhegaa jabaki sherkhan pathan, DSP disuja, abdul, padri, maaikel, dabid, aadi jaise adarsh charitra dekhne ko milenge. 8/ ho saktaa he aapane pehle kabhi is par dhyaan na diya ho, lekin abaki baar zaraa dhyaan se dekhnaa keval 'saleem/javed' kii hi nahin, balki kadar khan, kaifi azmi, mahesh bhatta, aadi kii filmon kaa bhi yahi haal he. 9/ film industry par daaud jaison kaa niyantran rahaa he. isamen aksar aparaadhiyon kaa mahimamandan kiya jaataa he or 'pandit' ko dhoort, thakur ko jaalim, 'banie' ko soodakhor, 'sardaar' ko murkh kamedian aadi hi dikhaaya jaataa he. 10/ 'farhaan akhtar' kii film "bhaag milkha bhaag" main 'havan karenge' kaa aakhir kya matlab tha? 11/ pk main bhagwaan kaa rong number bataane vaale aamir khan kya kabhi allaah ke rong number par bhi koi film banaayenge? meraa maananaa he ki- "yah sab mahaj ittefaq nahin he, balki sochi-samajhi sajeesh he !!!"

meerut ke civil lines ilaake main retoverd karnal devendra kumaar ke ghar chhapemari main 150 se adhik hathiyaar jisamen 40 raifal, 20 pistal, 2 lakh kaartoos, 1 karod nakad, 117 kilo pratibandhit maance mila he. media ko jis tarah se is khabar ko dikhaanaa tha usne vaise nahin dikhaaya. ab maan lijie retoverd karnal koi musalmaan hota. to desh kaa haal kaisaa hota? -NIA turant is maamle kii padtaal ke liye meerut pahunch chuki hoti. - grahamantri is puure maamle par pradhanmantri ko shwetapatr jari kar chuke hote. - ghar ke maalik, karnal ke rishtedaar, padosi or kutton tak ko police giraftaar kar chuki hoti. -media ab tak karnal ke taar ISIS, alqaida, hijbul, pakistan se jod chuki hoti. zee news har ek ghante main is par special report kar chukaa hota. abeepi news darjanon dibet karvaa chukaa hota. - rashtriya suraksha par likhane vaale sampadak/patrkaar ab tak us retoverd karnal kii bivi ke paas kitne peticot or kitne salwar kameez hai us par likh chuke hote. -soshal media par 'saare musalmaan aatankwaadi nahin hote lekin saare aatankwaadi musalmaan hote hai' kahana shuru ho gaya hota. farji news websites jeenyu ko iskaa zimmedaar bana chuke hote. chunki giraftaar karnal kaa naam devendra kumaar he na ki ashraf hossain isliye maahaul shant he. media aaraam se he. desh kii suraksha ko koi khatara nahin he. meerut pakistan nahin bana he. jai bharat. jai modi. jai media. jai rashtrawaad.

"jab hamaari rosemara kii zindagi main milane vaale log "savarna" yaa "dalit" nahin hote to phir kya vajah he ki "chunaav" aate hi ham "savarna" yaa "dalit" bana die jate hai ? aaj jis prakaar se nae noton kii karency badi rakam main pakadi ja rahi he ek bahut bada prashnchinh laga rahi he hamaare system or hamaare desh kii sarkaar par jahaan ek aam aadmi ek ek rupaye ke liye line main dhakke kha rahaa he vahiin duusari ore karodon kii nai karency kii baramadagi ye kehane ke liye kaaphi he ki is samay desh main kuch bhi acha nahin chal rahaa he bahut badi jaanch kaa vishay he ye ki ye nai karency bainkon ke alawa bhi kahin or se idhar udhar to nahin ho rahi . ab prashn ye he ki is notebandi kii prakriya main sirf or sirf ek aam aadmi hi pis rahaa he shaayad 50 din ke baad bhi pisna us aam aadmi kii niyati main shaamil rahegaa sarkaar sirf or sirf muhaavaron se or jumalon se or bhaashan se janata ko bahala rahi he or rashtrawaad kii duhai bhi di ja rahi he jo apni takalif bataanaa chahta he use deshadrohi kaha ja rahaa he aaj cash lash kii jis prakaar duhai di ja rahi he kya sarkaar ko ye pataa he ki desh main sakshartaa kaa kitna aankada he or nirakshartaa kaa aankada kitna he yahaan bhi sarkaar apni kamiyaan chupa rahi he janata kii swatantrata kaa bhi hanan ho rahaa he rashtrawaad kii aad main ye logon par nirbhar hona chahie ki wo apana ru cash se kharch karen yaa card se kharch karen or phir hamaare desh main kitna sakshartaa or kitna nirakshartaa kaa aankada he kya sarkaar ye bhi jaanati he kya cash lesh kii vakaalat karne vaali sarkaar ne sibar krime ko rokane kaa puraa intjaam kar liya he kya jo nirakshar log he wo cash lash paddati se havers ke saft target nahin honge phir vahi baat yani har kaam main adhuri taiyaari jaise notebandi thopi gayi ab cash lash kii baat kah janata par apni manamaani thopane kaa prayaas ho rahaa he . or shaayad aage sarkaar aam aadmi ke khaane pine uthne baithne kaa bhi minu tay kar de to koi aashcharya nahin hona chahie main sarkaar se poochna chahta hoon ki kya bhukh lagane par roti maangana deshadroh he ? kya dard hone par dawaai maangana deshadroh he ? kya apni takalif ko bataanaa deshadroh he ? hakeekat ye he ki sirf or sirf rashtrawaad kii aad lekar sarkaar apane adoordarshee faisle ko sahi sabit karne kii ji tod koshish main lagi he jabaki sarkaar bhi jaanati he ki unka ye notebandi kaa formula super flop sabit hua he kyonki unke is formule ne ek aam aadmi ko dard takalif or maansik yantranaa ke alawa kuch nahin diya

*kejariwal ke naam ek IIT ke ejeeniyar kaa khulaa patr* shriman aravind kejariwal ji, vaise saamanyatya main aapako gambhirtha se nahin letaa. parantu aaj mujhe aapkaa kuch kaha vyaktigat rup se bura laga he. aap ne kaha kii aap "IIT ke ejeeniyar" he, to EVM ko hack karne ke 10 tareeke bataa sakate he . main bhi IIT kaa ejeeniyar (Electrical) hoon or main aapako is santhaan kii izzat mitti main nahin milaane duungaa. aaj aapako kuch tathyon se saamana karwaata hoon. aapane aaj se kareeb 25 saal pehle IIT khadgpur se mecanical ejineering kiya. aap janata ko bevakoof bana sakate he par ek ejeeniyar ko nahin. ek mecanical ejeeniyar hone ke naate aap EVM ke bare main kuch nahin jaanate. EVM ke bare main gyaan hone ke liye aapako IC Design, Material science, Communication system, Electronics, Embedded system, Microprocessors and Programming ka knowledge hona jaruri hai . ejeeniyar to samanyatya 2 saal main sab bhul jate he agar unka naata ejineering se tut gaya ho or aap ko to 25 saal biit chuke he, isliye "IIT kaa ejeeniyar" hone ke naam par logon ko bevakoof bananaa band kijiye. aap jaanate bhi he EVM kaise kaam karata he? EVM ek Stand-alone mashin he, iskaa baahar kii duniya se koi naata nahin, ise Software ke madhyam se hack karnaa to lagbhag naammumkin he. haan agar koi jake chip badal aaye to sambhav he, isko rokane ke liye bhi chunaav ayog aavashyak prashasnic kadam uthaata he. aap ek haare huve rajaneta ke rup main EVM par prashn uthaayen par ek "IIT kaa ejeeniyar" hone ke naate nahin. vaise ek satya ye bhi he kii koi IIT kaa ho jane maatr se acha ejeeniyar nahin ho jaataa. achche ejeeniyar to wo he jinhone EVM jaisi mashin banaayin , or iskaa ek ek hissaa purna rup se bhartiya banaaya taaki kisi videshi ko bhi na pataa chal paae kii EVM kaise kaam karti he . ek hindi news channel ke jane mane patrkaar rajat sharma ne aapako IIT kaa Manufacturing Defect qaraar diya . kuch to shame karo, IITs kii kitni bejjati karwaaoge. khayr phir bhi aap ko lagata he kii EVM hack ho sakati he to ye gadhe kii tarah dhenchu dhenchu karnaa band karo . chunaav ayog ne sabhi ko nimatran diya he, aap bhi jaaen , aapke 10 main se koi 1 tarika lagaaein , EVM hack karen or janata ko siddh karen . ek baar hack karke dikhaao, phir kaho main IIT se hoon to hamen bhi acha lagegaa kii IIT ke mecanical ejeeniyar ne Electrical , electronics, material science, iti ejeeniyar sab ko galat sabit kar diya. desh kaa bhi bhala hoga, pataa to chalegaa kii system main kya badlaav jaruri he ise or phulpruf banane ke liye. par ejeeniyar hone ke baavjood bhi aap puraani or bhi ghatiya bailat paddati se chunaav kii maang kar rahe, ye to puri ejeeniyar community ke liye sharmnaak he. ejeeniyar technology ke maamle main kabhi peeche mud ke nahin dekhte. aapkaa shubhachintak, *gaurav, IIT dilli* kejariwal ji , chunaav ayog , ek vaidhanik swaayat sanstha he , jisaki vishwa me apni vishwasniyata he or jo kisi modi yaa kejariwal ke haath bik nahi sakati \u104a aap jaise aate -jate rahenge \u104a desh ko banaaye rakhane ke liye ye sansthaae jaruri he \u104a krupa apni gandi raajnneeti se inhen badnaam naa karen \u104a

Shivgami devi ne use vachan de diya fir devsena ke rajya me shadi kelie sandesh bhej diya Devsena ne mana kr diya ispe bharak ke shiv gami devi ne devsena ke rajya pe hamla kar diya Bahubali ne devsena ke rajya ko bacha liya aur dono me pyaar ho gya Bahubali ko laga ki shivgami devi ne usse shadi kelie sandesh bheja tha Isliye wo devsena ko leke mahismati aa jata h fir sacchai pta chalti h to shiv gami devi ne bola ki wo apna wachan ni tod sakti Isliye ya to bahubali ko devsena milegi ya fir raj gaddi Bahubali senapati bnn jata h Fir ak din bhallaldev ne bahubali ko senapati ke pad se nikal diya idhar devsena ke pregnant hone ki baat pta chlti h naya senapati bada badtameez hota h wo devsena ko pareshan krne ki kosis krta h Devsena uski ungli kaat deti h Fir devsena ko bandi bna kr raj mahal laya jata h Bahubali aata h use bachane Jb use pata chalata h ki senapati ne devsena ke sath badtimiziki wo use maar dena h Bahubali ko bhare shabha me senapati ko marne ke jurm me raj bhawan se bahar nikal dete h Bahubali khushi se mahesmati ke logon ke sath rhne lagta h usko janta bahut support krti h bhallaldev Bahubali ko marwane kelie apne admi bhejta h lekin wo ni mar pata Ye bat Bahubali ke ak dost ko pata chal jata h Wo uska picha krte krte mahesmati chla jata h Wahan use pata chalta h ki bhallaldev apne baap ka v sath chor chuka h Aurwo Bahubali ko marna chahta h Bhallaldev ka baap usko bolta h ki tum Bahubali ko bologe ki uska bhai usko marna chahta h to wo viswas ni krega Isliye Bahubali ko bachane kelie tum bhallaldev ko mardo Bhallaldev aur uske papa mile rhte h jab Bahubali ka dost bhallaldev ko marne jata h to usko maar dete h aur shivgami devi ko khte h ki Bahubali ne bhallaldev ko matne kelie isko bheja tha aur jo raja ka virodh kre usko marna pdega Shivgami devi bahubali ko marne katappa ko bolti h Katappa mana kr deta h Fir wo bolti h ki agar tum ni maroge to main mar dungi Katappa ko rajdroh ke jurm me mrityu dand milti h Bahubali ko ye pata chal jata h wo katappa ko bachane jata h idhar devsena maa bnne wali rahti hai Bahubali katappa ko bacha leta hai Tabhi kalkeya ka bhai aa jata h aur maheshmati pe akraman kr deta h Bahubali unkohara deta h usi waqt katappa usko maar deta h fir bhallaldev dev aata h aur wo galti se katappa ke samne hee sab sach bol deta h Katappa sb jake shivgami devi ko batati h Shivgami devi fir Bahubali ke bete ko raja bna deti h Bhallaldev unko marne kelie jata h Katappa shivgami devi aur mahendra Bahubali ko bacha leta h aur maheshmati se bhaga deta h Ye sb jaan ke mahendra Bahubali maheshmati pe akram kr deta h aur bhallaldev ko maar deta h The End

"kya din bhar main usne kisi se poocha ki bhai, tu "hindu" he yaa "musalmaan" ? agar tu "hindu" yaa "musalmaan" he to main teri bas main safar nahin karunga, tere haath kii chaay nahin piyunga, teri dukaan se toffee nahin kharidoongaa, kya usne sabun, doodh, aataa, namak, kapade, juute, akhbaar, toffee, mithai kharidte samay kisi se ye sawaal kiya tha ki ye sab banane or ugane vaale "hindu" hai yaa "musalmaan" ?
